    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without the 'new car' price tag. Everything runs smoothly, and I\u2019ve taken great care of it. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I do!",
