      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my reliable ride. It\u2019s been a fantastic car for me and is still in really wonderful shape! It drives super smoothly and has a very clean, comfortable interior that\u2019s perfect for your daily commute or a fun weekend getaway. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with everything, so it's ready to hit the road whenever you are. I\u2019d love for this to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have\u2014feel free to send me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 32500.0,
