      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This FD3S chassis represents the pinnacle of 90s JDM engineering, featuring the iconic 13B-REW twin-rotor engine. The sequential twin-turbocharger system has been meticulously maintained to ensure a seamless transition between the primary and secondary turbines, delivering a linear power band and sharp throttle response. Power is delivered through a crisp five-speed manual transmission to a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal traction during high-lateral-G cornering. The four-wheel double-wishbone suspension remains tight, preserving the car's legendary 50:50 weight distribution and communicative steering rack. Recent preventative maintenance includes a cooling system refresh and a comprehensive vacuum line overhaul to ensure the complex sequential boost control operates within factory parameters. This is a mechanically sound, driver-focused example for the purist who values visceral feedback and engineering pedigree.",
      "price": 34500.0,
